{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Note: After multiple updates and months of zero sales, I'm no longer updating this game and have dropped the price to $3. It's about 1-2 hours long without using the level editor. Thank you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hi, I'm Bowser, a solo indie dev. I wanted to create something that exists somewhere between a game, a maker game, and a game engine, a toy box that can be enjoyed by casual players, skilled players, level designers, modders, rom hackers, and everyone in-between. Built from the ground up on a custom engine designed for level making and modding, with pixel perfect rendering, dynamic lighting, and a retro physics engine. Full game, not early access, no in-app purchases, no DLC, and I'm committed to regular updates, with at least a few new things for the editor each week.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full controller support. Designed for cozy couch gaming. No mouse or keyboard needed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332260/extras/Segment_625.gif?t=1731994862\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc2f Features \ud83d\udc2f</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run, jump, swim, fly, carry, throw, and roll around in a vibrant world full of secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique shake mechanic changes how you interact with your environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Includes a story mode with 10 levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Includes an in-game level editor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Built on a custom game engine designed from the ground up for modding.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Includes an easy-to-use C# SDK, allowing anyone to create new objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High framerate support, up to 240Hz.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievements. Cloud saves.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc2f Editor Features \ud83d\udc2f</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build on a map 20x bigger than Super Mario Maker.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build with no arbitrary limits on the number of objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Select from over 200 objects, with over 25 enemies, or make your own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place slopes, water, and decoration anywhere you want.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place signs with text to guide the player or tell a story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Place objects on different Z layers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Design complex puzzles using switches, wires, and logic blocks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create atmosphere with colorful and interactive lighting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Control the camera with rooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix and match different background layers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add weather effects and post-processing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make blocky pixel art within your levels.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc2f Steam Workshop Features \ud83d\udc2f</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Subscribe to new objects, backgrounds, foregrounds, and other mods.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easily publish your own creations to the Steam Workshop from within the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Package mods with levels to provide players with a rom-hack-like experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc2f Online Features \ud83d\udc2f</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upload levels and share them using a code.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Browse uploaded levels on the Discord server.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You do not need to create an account and the game does not require an internet connection.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To mod the game, extract Sdk.zip in the install directory and read GettingStarted.md. Most people can run their first mod within minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332260/extras/Segment_801.gif?t=1731994862\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332260/extras/Segment_267.gif?t=1731994862\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332260/extras/Segment_351.gif?t=1731994862\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Started Game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/bf23ba49e5554c5ca4210aad05582cc265d0d24f.jpg"},{"name":"Viewed Ending","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/7d538c04dbff23de242c11a680c879c8bfd2709d.jpg"},{"name":"Viewed Credits","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/2a52c44e4c6616e47870df1b69f2d394d7156673.jpg"},{"name":"Opened Editor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/5b46abe424609f8767a1d21f32d0ccb5f0092653.jpg"},{"name":"Installed Mod","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/0d8b1d3e2a453da842c7b7bc1ac04588ddae6cf6.jpg"},{"name":"Started Save","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/ace5448e14383ccc63a477c018317aee1f1d8c04.jpg"},{"name":"Used Scene Code","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1332260/